Rank the latest generic agent-material dispatch results by win rate, Sharpe, then return

Usage: ict-engine auto-quant-agent-material-rank [OPTIONS] --symbol <SYMBOL>

Options:
      --symbol <SYMBOL>        Instrument identifier supplied by the caller
      --state-dir <STATE_DIR>  State directory holding generic agent-material artifacts [env: ICT_ENGINE_STATE_DIR=] [default: state]
  -h, --help                   Print help
